description: Mixed use redevelopment comprising: (a) outline planning permission for industrial development (3220 square metres floor space) and 37 Live-Work units (3950 square metres floorspace) on the western part of the site adjoining Sutherland Road and part of Stirling Road Path E17 and: (b)full planning permission for residential development on the remainder of the site adjoining Stirling road, Hillyfield and St. Andrews Road consisting of 241 residential units (105x1 bed, 117x2 bed, 17x3 bed and 2x4 bed) involving the erection of buildings ranging from between three and six storeys in height, provision of surface parking (22 spaces plus 4 integral garages) and basement car park (218 spaces) with entrances off St. Andrews Road and Stirling Road with exit only from Stirling Road.
